data.description:
Discover comfort and style in this charming 4 bed, 3 bath trilevel home situated on a corner lot in the JACK BRITT school district! The living area and kitchen boast exquisite wood beams, infusing rustic warmth into the open space. Elegant light fixtures grace each room, casting a captivating glow. Step outside to a private fenced patio, perfect for serene moments or enjoy the huge backyard! Enjoy the amazing location with convenient shopping close and a dog park close by for your furry family members to enjoy. Roof 2023. Revel in the updated flooring in the first floor bath and in the primary bath, blending modernity with coziness. This residence harmoniously merges modern updates with timeless features, offering a truly inviting retreat. Welcome Home!
